BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:sap-s4hana-watch-2026-w26@codex.local
DTSTAMP:20260629T080959Z
SUMMARY:SAP S/4HANA Cloud watch: W26 hotfix / patching
DTSTART:20260627T150000Z
DTEND:20260627T190000Z
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
LOCATION:SAP S/4HANA Cloud Public Edition online schedule
DESCRIPTION:SAP S/4HANA Cloud Public Edition 2602 HFC13 was released on 25.06.2026. SAP Note 3646210 includes 91 application corrections in attachment S4HANACloud2602HFC13_ListOfHotfixShortDescription.pdf.\n\nAreas include Ariba integration, migration cockpit, document compliance, Central Business Configuration, actual costing, service orders, localisation and DRC, group reporting, treasury, EWM, delivery APIs, product master, purchasing analytics, purchase orders, maintenance plans, production, PSM, QM, billing, freight and logistics integration.\n\nSAP announced final What's New and Product Assistance for SAP S/4HANA Cloud Public Edition 2602.4. SAP Help also lists 54 official 2602.4 (HFC12) What's New entries, all dated 26.06.2026 in search results. Tracked topics include Developer Extensibility for scheduling goods issue for deliveries, Explore Migration Objects enhancements, Joule features, project/work-package details, electronic invoicing, withholding-tax analysis, BOM print preview, quality inspection, and logistics/compliance updates. SAP recommends RASD for a personalized view based on activated and used scope; the announcement says 2602.4 information would be available in RASD within the next few days.\n\nTimezone shown to user: Australia/Sydney.\nCalendar status: Free.\nSource: SAP S/4HANA Cloud Public Edition, 3-System Landscape - Upgrade & Maintenance Schedule plus SAP Note 3646210, SAP Community final 2602.4 announcement, and SAP Help 2602.4 What's New/Product Assistance search results.\nCodex SAP maintenance watch id: 2026-W26
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-PT12H
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:SAP S/4HANA Cloud watch window reminder
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT
