UID:sap-s4hana-watch-2026-w33-dev@codex.local
DTSTAMP:20260629T080959Z
SUMMARY:SAP S/4HANA Cloud watch: 2608 Development upgrade
DTSTART:20260815T040000Z
DTEND:20260815T080000Z
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
LOCATION:SAP S/4HANA Cloud Public Edition online schedule
DESCRIPTION:2608 major upgrade for Development systems. SAP's 2608 upgrade guidance indicates D/P tenants upgrade with HFC03+ on 15-16 August 2026, with T-Tenant receiving HFC03+ in the same weekend. Preliminary 2608 What's New and Product Assistance content is available for upgrade preparation through the What's New Viewer and RASD. Customer action remains active: validate IAM successor app activation and transport role changes before Development and Production move to 2608. RASD impact-card follow-ups should also be validated before this weekend. Full HFC03+ attachment details are still pending until SAP publishes the 2608 patch collection note.\n\nTimezone shown to user: Australia/Sydney.\nCalendar status: Free.\nSource: SAP S/4HANA Cloud Public Edition, 3-System Landscape - Upgrade & Maintenance Schedule plus SAP 2608 upgrade guidance, preliminary 2608 What's New guidance, RASD 2026 update, and IAM app activation guidance.\nCodex SAP maintenance watch id: 2026-W33-DEV
